# KAN-<ticket>: <type>: <short summary>
#
# Types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, chore, test, ci
# Example: KAN-12: feat: add alert stats resolver
#
# Smart commits (auto-transition in Jira):
#   KAN-12 #in-progress   - moves ticket to In Progress
#   KAN-12 #done          - moves ticket to Done
#   KAN-12 #comment <text> - adds comment to ticket
